<br>
All on lvl0 mobs :<br>
<br>
2h Sword 14.1 DPS 4.5 SPD<br>
without style : 246 dmg<br>
with perforate : 726 dmg<br>
-------------------------<br>
bonus : 480 dmg<br>
<br>
1h Sword 14.6 DPS 2.5 SPD<br>
without style : 105 dmg<br>
with perforate : 585 dmg<br>
-------------------------<br>
bonus : 480 dmg<br>
<br>
But using a 2h axe :<br>
2h Axe 15.3 DPS 5.5 SPD<br>
without style : 281 dmg<br>
with perforate : 762 dmg<br>
------------------------<br>
bonus : 481 dmg<br>
<br>
<br>
Im not specced in axe, but im specced in sword so dunno where the 1 point different does come from (tested it several times). <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><br><font color=#FF0000>- </font><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse>The Safehouse</a><font color=#FF0000> - </font><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19>Main Hall</a> <font color=#FF0000> - </font><a href="http://www.thesafehouse.org">The Safehouse website</a><font color=#FF0000> - </font> <center><a href="http://www.guildboss.com"><img
